The paper discusses intrusion detection systems for networked UAVs, which involves security and networking aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
